## Notion setup

1. Duplicate workspace structure per [docs/NOTION_SETUP.md](docs/NOTION_SETUP.md)
2. Import CSVs from [data/notion-import/](data/notion-import/)
3. Upload evidence JSON from `evidence/` after each `sentinel run-all`

